WEBVTT

00:06.939 --> 00:08.173
- Uhh!

00:08.175 --> 00:09.041
Ooh!

00:10.977 --> 00:13.479
Uhh! Uhh!

00:13.481 --> 00:15.514
Ahh!

00:15.516 --> 00:17.116
- You're gonna break it.

00:17.118 --> 00:19.451
- I think I know
my own recliner.

00:19.453 --> 00:20.753
Sometimes it just sticks.

00:20.755 --> 00:22.921
Got to give it
a little uhh!

00:22.923 --> 00:24.923
Got to give it
a little aah!

00:24.925 --> 00:26.859
But sometimes it knows
you're gonna do that,

00:26.861 --> 00:30.863
So you've got to
surprise it with
a little hah!

00:30.865 --> 00:33.332
Hah! Hyah! Hah!

00:33.334 --> 00:34.767
Hyah! Hah!

00:37.237 --> 00:38.270
Wah!

00:38.272 --> 00:39.038
[crash]

00:39.040 --> 00:41.707
That's good.

